HEADWORD: Corrugant
<hw>Cor"ru*gant</hw> <pr>(k?r"r?-g<it>a</it>nt)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos>
<ety>[L. <ets>corrugans</ets>, p. pr. See <er>Corrugate</er>.]</ety>
<def>Having the power of contracting into wrinkles.</def>
<rj><au>Johnson.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

